casebody.head_matter:
Johnny Brett GREGORY, petitioner,
v.
Deborah DENHAM, Warden.
No. 14-10324.
Supreme Court of the United States
Oct. 5, 2015.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
Justice KAGAN took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.
